tafsir[60]{c,v,t}:
  30,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim: yewtere sugu …óee Aayeeje yawtiino ka fu…ó…óorde cortewol Al-Baqarah."
  30,2,"Faarisiyankoo…ìe …ìen foolii Ruumi'en."
  30,3,"Nde fooleede wa…óii ka Saami ka …ìuri …ìadorde leydi Faarisi ndin. Ruumiyankoo…ìe …ìen non, …ìaawo …ìe fooleede, …ìe fooloyay kam…ìe kadi."
  30,4,"Ngol kiitol ko wa…ói, ko e dumunna mo hewtaa duu…ìi tati o fawaa e duu…ìi sappo. Ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow ado poolgal Ruumiyakoo…ìe …ìen ngal e …ìaawo maggal. Nden √±alnde nde Ruumiyankoo…ìe …ìen fooloyta Faarisiyankoo…ìe …ìen, gom…óim…ìe …ìen weltoray."
  30,5,"∆Åe weltorayay ko Alla walliri Ruumiyankoo…ìe …ìen kon, tawde …ìen ko yim…ìe Defte. Alla no walla on Mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo Mo fooleaake, Hinnotoo…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko gom…óim…ìe …ìen."
  30,6,"Ngal balla ko fodoore Alla wonunoo. Laatagol mayre ngol …ìeyday gom…óim…ìe …ìen pellital e fodoore Alla nden. Kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe hino majjiraa …óum sabu keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe ngun."
  30,7,"∆Åe anndaa gom…óinal e √±aawooje sari'a. Ko …ìe anndii woo ko ko fee√±i e nguurndam aduna …óam e ko yowondiri e …óa…ì…ìere nguuree ma…ì…ìe e mahugol ngaddamaaku. Kono kam…ìe e fii laakara on won…óo ho…óo nguurndam …óam tigi, ko …ìe …óuurnii …ìe, …ìe tefataa fii mun."
  30,8,"E …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe miijitaaki fii no Alla tagiri wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe O fotindiri …ói? Alla tagiraali kammuli …óin e leydi ndin si wanaa goona, O tagiraali …ói fijindaaru, O wa…óanii …ói kadi lajal happaangal heddagol ka aduna. Anndee non, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen, ko yeddu…ìe hawroygol e Joomi ma…ì…ìe √ëalnde Darngal, ko …óum ha…ói …ìe hebloranagol nden √±alnde golle mo∆¥∆¥e weltinay…óe Joomi ma…ì…ìe."
  30,9,"E …ìee yiilaaki ka leydi …ìe taskoo ko honno battane mofte fennunoo…ìe …ìen ado ma…ì…ìe wa'unoo? ∆Åen laatino …ìur…ìe doole, …ìe wuurniti leydi ndin remuruuji, …ìe wuuri e mayri …ìuri ko …ìee wuuri e mayri kon. Nulaa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen addani …ìe hujjaaji …ìanngin…ói gootaaku Alla ngun, kono …ìe fenni. Alla too√±iraa …ìe halkugol …ìe ngol, kono non, ko ko'e ma…ì…ìe …ìe wonunoo e too√±irde jolnorgol jolirde halkaare sabu keefaraagu ma…ì…ìe ngun ."
  30,10,"Refti ko wonunoo battane …ìen bonnirnoo…ìe golle mun sirkangol Alla e golle bon…óe, ko bone …ìur…óo bondne; tawde …ìe fennii Aayeeje Alla …óen, …ìe laatii e jalkitugol …óe."
  30,11,"Ko Alla woni fu…ó…óir…óo tagu ngun no ngu ko aldah e yeru gadii…óo, refti O gayna fii maggu, refti O ruttita ngu; refti ko ka Makko Kanko tun ruttete…óon √ëalnde Darngal fii hasbeede yo…ìee."
  30,12,"√ëalnde Darngal ngal dorotoo, bombe …ìen ta∆¥oyto e yurmeende Alla, tawde hujja ma…ì…ìe e yeddugol Alla ngol wonii bolle puy…óe."
  30,13,"Woodanoytaa…ìe e kafidii…ói ma…ì…ìe …ói …ìe rewynoo …óin aduna, ko tefana …ìe da…óugol lepte …óen, wurin …óin yeddoyay kafidu…ìe…ói …ìen; …ói hoynoya …ìe ka …ìe hatonjinnoo e ma…ì…ìe, kono …ói hattanaa e, tawde …ìe fotay ka halkaare."
  30,14,"√ëalnde Darngal ngal darii, nden √±alnde yim…ìe …ìen sertiroyay e njo…ìdi yeru no …ìe gollirnoo aduna non: wo…ó…ìe towniroyee ka Aljannaaji dow, wo…ó…ìe jippiniroyee ley ka Yiite."
  30,15,"Si ko …ìen gom…óim…ìe Alla …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e weltinay…óe Mo, …ìen …óon wonoyay e beeli Aljanna hi…ìe weltiro ko …ìe neeminirtee ton e neemaaji duumotoo…ói poomaa."
  30,16,"Si tawii non ko …ìen yeddu…ìe Alla …ìe fenni Aayeeje Amen jippinaa…óe e Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, …ìe fenni kadi ummital e hasboore, …ìen …óon ko tawnoytee…ìe e lepte …óen …ìe lutta e majje."
  30,17,"Subbuhinanee Alla tuma naatanton kiikii…óe; …óum woni fewndo julde futuroo e gee∆¥e, subbunhinano…óon Mo kadi tuma naatanton bimmbi; …óum ko fewndo julde subaka nden."
  30,18,"Ko Kanko Alla tun mantoore woodani: Malaa'ika'en no yetta Mo ka kammuuli, tagu ngun kadi no yettira Mo ka leydi. Subbunhinane Mo saanga naatanton kiikii…óe, …óum woni fewndo ka Alansaraa, subbunhinan…óon Mo kadi saanga √±allonton, …óum woni fewndo ka fanaa."
  30,19,"Himo yaltina ko wuuri e nder ko maayi; wano tagirgol ne…ó…óo immorde e to…ì…ìere maniiyu maa yaltinirgol cofun e nder woofoonde, Himo yaltina kadi ko maayi e nder ko wuuri, wano tagirgol Mo to…ì…ìere maniiyu nden immorde e ne…ó…óo maa woofoonde nden immorde e gertogal ngal. Himo wuurnitira leydi ndin jippingol to…ìo fu…óina ndi …ìaawo ndi yoorude. Ko wano ndin leydi wuurnitiraa non fu…óingol ndi, yaltinirte…óon e genaale maon fii hasbeede yo…ìee."
  30,20,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Alla maw…ói tinndin…ói kattal Makko ngal e gootankaaku Makko ngun: wonde O tagii mon onon …ìee yim…ìe, immorde e mbum-mbuldi, fewndo O tagirnoo ben Aadama e loopal, refti jaka ko on …ìanndinke saakitoray…ìe …óuu…óal, saakito…óon hiirnaange e fu…ónaange leydi ndin."
  30,21,"Hino jeyaa fahin e maandeeji Alla maw…ói tinndinay- …ói kattal e gootaaku Makko, wonnde O taganii on, onon wor…ìe …ìen, immorde e noone mon, resondir- …ìe, fii yo on dee∆¥ir e ma…ì…ìe tawde ko on noone gooto, O wa…ói hakkunde mon giggol e yurmeende. Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói wonannde yim…ìe miijitotoo…ìe, tawde ko kam…ìe nafitorta gollitirgol haqqil."
  30,22,"Hino jeyaa kadi e maandeeji Alla …óin tinndin…ói kattal e gootaaku Makko, tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e luutondirgol haalaaji mon e nooneeji mon. Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji …ìanngan…ói yim…ìe anndal e tasakuyee …ìen."
  30,23,"Hino jeyaa kadi e maandeeji Makko maw…ói tinnin- …ói kattal e gootaaku Makko: …óoyngol mon ngol jemma e √±alorma, fii fowtagol e ronkere golle mon. Hino jeyaa e majji fahin, ko O wa…óirani on √±alorma on kon saakitagol e makko …óa…ì…ìira Joomi mon arsike. Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói, wonannde yim…ìe nanoo…ìe nanugol taskoo e nanugol ja…ìde."
  30,24,"Hino jeyaa kadi e maandeeji Makko maw…óit inndi- tnay…ói kattal e gootaaku Makko, hollirgol on ma∆¥e …óen ka kammu; O hawtitana on e …óum, hakkunde kulol par√±ite …óen e tama'u to…ìo ngon. Himo jippini- ra kadi ka kammu ndiyam to…ìo, O wuurnitira …óam leydi ndin, fu…óingol pu…ói e mayri, …ìaawo ndi yoorde Wonii e ko jantaa koo, hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói, wonande yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe, …ìe dallinora …óum ummital …ìaawo maayde, fii hasbeede yo…ìee."
  30,25,"Hino jeyaa e maandeji Makko tindin…ói kattal e gootaaku Makko: tawde kammu ngun e leydi ndin no darorii yamiroore Makko ko aldaa e yanugol. Refti si o noddii noddaandu wutttugol Mala'ikaajo on allaandu ndu ka leydi, e jaka onon hi…óon yaltira e genaale mon …óen hasbeede yo…ìee."
  30,26,"Ko kanko tun woodani, laamagol e tagugol e toppital …ìen won…ìe ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Kala kon ko tagaa, ko …óoftii…ìe Mo jebbilanii yamiroore Makko."
  30,27,"Ko Kanko woni fu…ó…óor…óo tagugol ngol no ko aldah, e yeru gadii…óo refti O ruttita ngu …ìaawo gaynugol fii maggu. Awa fu…ó…óitagol ngol hino …ìuri fu…ó…óagol ngol welde fii, fow mun, …óin …ói…ói kala hino newanii Alla; tawde si O faandanike huunde, O daalanay nde tun: ""Laato"", nde laatoo. Hino woodani Mo Kanko teddu…óo maw…óo On, sifa …ìur…óo toowude on e kala ko O sifortee e sifaaji mawngu e timmal. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo Mo fooletaak, √ëee√±u…óo e tagu Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  30,28,"O piyanii on misal, onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, ∆¥ettaangal e mon: Hara no woodani on e maccu…ìe mon …ìen e …ìen jeytir…óon √±aame mon renndaa…óo e jawle mon …óen, …ìe huloton senndodugol …óen jewle e mon, wano hulirton senndodugol e dimo hawtidu…óo e mon jawle? Hara on ja…ìanay …óum maccu…óo mon? Pellet on ja…ìataa …óum. Awa ko Alla …ìuri hanndude nde O ja…ìataa kafideede e tagu Makko (jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen) ka laamu Makko. Ko wano ngal misal piyirani mon, ngam Men …ìanngina hujjaaji e …ìanngannduyeeji sertu…ói, wonnde yim…ìe haqqil…ìe, tawde ko kam…ìe nafitorta …óum."
  30,29,"Wanaa waasde dalil woni sabu majjere ma…ì…ìe, wanaa waaseede …ìannginannede kadi. Majjere ma…ì…ìe nden, ko sabu jokkugol mbelee…óe e √±emmbugol baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe. Ko hommbo non fewnata mo Alla majjini? Hay gooto! Alanaa …ìe walloo…ìe ko du√±ana …ìe lepte Alla …óen."
  30,30,"Fewtiniri yeeso maa ngon, an Nulaa…óo e wondu- …ìe e maa …ìen, e diina Alla kan; acca kala diina si wanaa diina Makko kan. ∆äum ko diina lislaamu mo Alla tagiri yim…ìe …ìen e mun. Wa…ótitugol alaa e tagu Alla ngun. Ko …óum woni diina focciika kan; kono …ìur…ìe …óuu…óude e yim…ìe anndaa wonnde ko …óum woni diina goonga."
  30,31,"Ruttoree e Makko tuubugol e junuubi mon, huliron Mo …óoftagol yamirooje Makko wo…ó…óitoo ha…óaa…ói Makko, √±inniron julde nden no timmiri, wata on jeye e sirkoo…ìe lunndii…ìe tagoodi ndin; …ìe kafida Alla e wo…ó…ìe goo ka dewe ma…ì…ìe,"
  30,32,"Wata on wa'u wa …ìen sirkoo…ìe waylunoo…ìe diina mun, …ìe goom…óini yoga …ìe yeddi yoga, …ìe wonti pecce-pecce, fedde kala e ma…ì…ìe no weltora meere wonnde ka ma…ì…ìe nden, kala yi'a ko ka√±um tun woni e goonga, …ìeya kan ko e meere woni."
  30,33,"Si sa…óteende memii sirkoo…ìe …ìen, immorde e √±awu maa baasal maa kokke, …ìe nodda Joomi ma…ì…ìe tun, ruttitorgol e Makko yankinagol moolo e makko, fii no O huncirana …ìe sa…óteende ma…ì…ìe. Hooti si O yurmiraama …ìe huncangol …ìe nden sa…óteende, e jaka fedde e ma…ì…ìe hino yiltitoo e sirkangol kafida Joomi mun e go…ó…óum goo ka du'agol."
  30,34,"Si …ìe yeddi neemaaji Alla …óin, wano yeddugol …ìe neema huncaneede sa…óteende nden, wonii …ìe dakmitorii ko …ìe jogitii e …óam nguurndam, arma …ìe yi'iroya gite ma…ì…ìe …óen √ëalnde Darngal, wonnde ko e majjere …ìanngunde …ìe wonunoo e mun."
  30,35,"Ko naadi …ìe e sirkangol Alla ko aldaa e hujja? Menen, Men jippinaali e ma…ì…ìe hujja Deftere, mo …ìe dallinorta e ko …ìe sirkanta Alla kon. ∆Åe alaa kadi deftere yewtaynde fii sirku ma…ì…ìe on, qirritantoonde …ìe sellugol ko …ìe yeddaynoo kon."
  30,36,"Si Men mee…óinirii yim…ìe …ìen gootel e neemaaji Amen …óin, wano cellal e ngalu, …ìe weltora …óum weltaare dullere e townitaare. Si tawnii non ko bone on memirii …ìe - wano √±awu e baasal - sabu ko juu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen faggitori kon geddi, …óum haray …ìe ta∆¥ike yurmeende Alla nden, …ìe sikka …óum …óon iwataa e ma…ì…ìe."
  30,37,"E …ìee yi'aali, wonnde Alla no ya√±√±ana arsike on mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, fii ndaarnda- gol …ìe si …ìe yettay Mo maa si …ìe yedday? Himo …ìi…ótinana Mo kadi on Mo O muuyani e ma…ì…ìe, fii anndugol si o mu√±√±oto maa o mu√±√±oo? Wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde gom…óim…ìe neweende e yurmeende Alla nden."
  30,38,"An juul…óo on, jonnu jom-…ìadal ngal ko o haandi ko, ka mo∆¥∆¥ugol e ka jokkugol en…óam, okkaa hatonjin…óo kadi ko humtanta mo haaju mum, walla-…óaa tumarankeejo wo…ó…óitii…óo leydi mun. Ko ngool okkugol e …óeen geece …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude wonande …ìen faalaa…ìe yarluyee Alla on; ko …ìen huntoo…ìe …óin haajuuji kadi, woni maliroytee…ìe he…ìugol Aljanna mo …ìe …óa…ì…ìaynoo, …ìe hisa e lepte …óe …ìe hulunoo."
  30,39,"Kala ko jonnir…óon yim…ìe …ìen e jawle, fii no …óe artira e mon …ìeydaari(riba), annde …óe …ìeydotaako ka Alla. Kala non ko jonnir…óon e jawle mon …óen, fii ko duncitoree haaju, hara hi…óon …óa…ì…ìira …óum yarluyee Alla, wanaa darja maa manteede, ko …ìen …óon woni sowanoytee…ìe njo…ìdi ka Alla."
  30,40,"Ko Alla gooto On hertori tagugol on, refti arsikugol on, refti warugol on wuurnita. Hara no e sanamuuji mon, …ói rewoton gaanin Makko …óin, wa…óayndu go…ó…óum e …óin? Senayee woodanii Mo! O toowii e ko sirkoo…ìe …ìen wowlata …ìe fi…ìa."
  30,41,"Bone on fee√±irii ka njorndi e ka maaje, …óuytagol nguurndam yim…ìe …ìen e wonkiiji ma…ì…ìe, nawnaaje e √±abbuuli; sabu ko …ìe golli e geddi. ∆äum fee√±irii fii no Alla mee…óinira …ìe njo…ìdi yoga e ko …ìe bonnuno e nguurndam aduna …óam; belajo'o, …ìe ruttoray e Makko tuubugol."
  30,42,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan …ìee sirkoo…ìe: Yiilee ka leydi, tasko…óon ko honno battane mofte fennunoo…ìe adinoo…ìe on …ìen wa'unoo. ∆äum ko battane bon…óe wonunoo, tawde ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe ko sirkanaynoo…ìe Alla, …ìe halkiraa sabu …óum."
  30,43,"An Nulaa…óo, fewtinir yeeso maa ngon e diina lislaamu focciika kan, ado √ëalnde Darngal arde nde ruttoowo nde alaa. Nden √±alnde, yim…ìe …ìen seedoya: fedde goo neeminiree ka Aljanna, ndeya fedde leptiroyee ka Yiite."
  30,44,"Kala yeddu…óo Alla, lorra mun - woni luttugol ka Yiite - ko e makko yantata. Kala non gollu…óo mo∆¥∆¥ere, nde o …óa…ì…ìiri welayee Alla e mun, haray …ìen …óon, ko ko'e-ma…ì…ìe …ìe hebilani naatugol Aljanna, …ìe neeminora duumagol ton poomaa."
  30,45,"Ko fii no Alla yo…ìira gom…óim…ìe Mo …ìen, …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥u…ói welay…ói Joomi ma…ì…ìe. Pellet, Kanko senii…óo On, O yi…óaa yeddidu…ìe Mo e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen, hi…ìe metta Mo sanne, O leptoyay …ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  30,46,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Alla maw…ói, tinn…óinay…ói kattal e gootaaku Makko, wurtugol Mo keneeli wewliniray…ói jeyaa…ìe …ìen, hewtugol to…ìo ngon, e fii yo O mee…óinir on, onon yim…ìe …ìen, yurmeende Makko nden, he…ìugol mo∆¥∆¥ere to…ìo ngon, woni ... O wa…óiri …óum kadi, no laa…óe …óen dogira muuyaa…óe Makko, e fii no …óa…ì…ìiron e …ìural Makko ngal, ngeygu ka maaje, belajo'o, on yettay neemaaji Alla …óin e moo…óon, O …ìeydana on."
  30,47,"Gom…óii Men nulii ado maa an Nulaa…óo, Nulaa…ìe goo, haa e mofte ma…ì…ìe …óen, …ìe addani …ìe hujjaaji …ìanngin…ói gonnga ma…ì…ìe kan, kono …ìeya fenni …ìe. Men yottii ontuma e …ìen faggitii…ìe geddi, Men halkiri …ìe lepte Amen …óen, Men da…óndi Nulaa…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe wondunoo…ìe e ma…ì…ìe …ìen. Da…óndugol gom…óime …ìen, faaboo …ìe, ko ko Men wa…ó…óini e Amen."
  30,48,"Ko Alla woni nuloowo immina keneeli …óin, …ói sogga duule …óen; O saakitira …óum ka weeyo no O muuyiri, …óuu…ói fan…ói; O wa…óta …óum ta∆¥e-ta∆¥e. A yi'ay ontuma, an ndaaroowo on, to…ìo ngon no yalta hakkunde mun. Si O hewtinii to…ìo ngon e on Mo O muuyi e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, e jaka hi…ìe weltora yurmeende Alla nden e ma…ì…ìe, woni he…ìugol to…ìo, leydi ndin fu…óina ko …ìe haajitora kam…ìe e neemoraa…ói ma…ì…ìe."
  30,49,"Gom…óii …ìe laatinoke ado Alla jippinde to…ìo ngon e ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìe ta∆¥inoo…ìe e …óum."
  30,50,"Ndaarii an Nulaa…óo, battane to…ìo ngo Alla jippiniri yurmeende e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen, no O wuurnitirta leydi ndin noone e pu…ói, …ìaawo ndii cojjii ndi yoori. Pellet, wa…óu…óo …óum On, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ìe …ìen, Kanko ko O hattan…óo kala huunde, huunde ronkintaa Mo."
  30,51,"sI Men nulii henndu e gese maa e pu…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin ko bonna fii mun, …ìe yi'i …óen gese ma…ì…ìe no soy…óa …ìaawo nde …óe hecci…óunoo, …ìe wa…ótinay …ìaawo …óum, ko …ìe yeddoo…ìe neemaaji Alla yawtu…ói …óin, e …óuu…óugol majji."
  30,52,"Ko wano woniri non a nanintaa maay…ìe …ìen e faa…óu…ìe …ìen, wo…ó…óitorii …ìe ma fii wata …ìe nane few, ko wano non woniri a waawataa fewnude nanndo ma…ì…ìe, …óuurn…óii…óo salii…óo he…óitaade."
  30,53,"A wonaali fewnoo mo Alla majjini e laawol focciingol ngol, a nanintaa ko nafata, si wanaa on gom…óiin…óo Aayeeje Amen …óen, tawde ko kanko nafitorta ko wowlata, …ìen, ko jebbilanii…ìe Men, yankinii…ìe."
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo on, onon …ìee yim…ìe, immorde e ndihal hoykal, refi O wa…ói …ìaawo lo'ere mon entereyaagal nden, cemmbe sagatalaaku, refi O wa…ói …ìaawo …óen cemmbe, lo'ere nayeegu. Alla hino taga ko O yi…ói, immorde e ko lo'i maa ko dolni. Ko Kano woni Anndu…óo kala huunde, huunde ronkintaa Mo. Hattan…óo Mo huunde ronkintaa."
  30,55,"√ëalnde Darangal ngal drotoo, bom…ìe …ìen hu…óoto …ìe √±ii…ìaali ka genaale ma…ì…ìe si wanaa saanga. Ko wano …ìe ferlisiraa e anndugol happu √±ii…ìugol ma…ì…ìe ngol ka genaale, …ìe wonanoo e firliteede aduna, gaayi e goonga."
  30,56,"∆Åen Annabaa…ìe e Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìe Alla okki ganndal …ìen wi'a: Gom…óii on √±ii…ìii e ko Alla winndi kon e ganndal Makko ngal, gila √±alnde taga…óon haa √±alde ummital mon ngal yeddu…óon. Kono onon on anndaano wonnde ummital ko wa…óay…óum, yeddu…óon …óum."
  30,57,"√ëalnde Alla immintinoyta tagu ngun, fii hasbeede yo…ìitee, ngantooji …ói too√±u…ìe …ìen fefindoytoo …óin nafoytaa …ìe, wanaa kam…ìe woni ko …óa…ì…ìirtee weltingol Alla, sakko …ìe ja…ìanee tuubugol ruttoo e Makko, tawde haray laawiki!"
  30,58,"Gom…óii Men piyanii yim…ìe …ìen e ndee Alqur'aanaare, ko toppitagol fii ma…ì…ìe, kala misal. ∆äum, ko fii no goonga fee√±irana …ìe e nder meere nden. Pellet, si a addanii …ìe, an Nulaa…óo, hujja goonga maa kan, ma …ìen yeddu…ìe Alla wi'u: On wonaali, si wanaa meerentee…ìe e ko addu…óon kon."
  30,59,"Ko wano …ìer…óe …ìee …ìe tawata si a addanii…ìe Aaya …ìe gom…óintaa, Alla notiraa e …ìenrde kala …ìe anndaa wonnde ko addan-…óaa…ìe kon, ko goonga."
  30,60,"Mu√±√±o an Nulaa…óo, e ko yim…ìe maa …ìen fennete kon. Anndaa pellet, fodoore Alla faabo e foolde, ko laatotoo…óum sikke alaa. Wata dunyma …ìe yananaaka e ummital …ìen du√±e e hawjugol, ronkaa mu√±√±aade."
